import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'

const BodyPart = () => {
  return (
    <>
       <Container fluid>
         <Row>
            <Col xl={12} lg={12} md={12} sm={12} >
            <Col xl={12} lg={12} md={12} sm={12} >
                
            </Col>
            </Col>
         </Row>
       </Container>

    </>
  )
}

export default BodyPart
